data.description: Bring your offers! This property is priced to go and seller is ready to sell asap! Selling as-is. This 4-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom Cape Cod style house with a two-car attached garage is a gem that perfectly blends classic charm with modern updates. Ideal for homeowners as well as property investors, this residence has recently been remodeled to provide both character and convenience with fresh paint throughout and brand new carpeting in all bedrooms, upstairs hallways and stairwell. The thoughtfully updated living spaces are spacious and welcoming. Nestled on a corner lot in a sought-after neighborhood, this home is conveniently located near schools and shopping centers, an excellent choice for those looking to establish a comfortable home or investors seeking an attractive addition to their real estate portfolio. 1st floor laundry. Across the street from Willow Park!
